        "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified-1\n\nBuild Failed \n\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/job/offline-installer-master-yaml-lint/22/ : FAILURE\n\nNo problems were identified. If you know why this problem occurred, please add a suitable Cause for it. ( https://jenkins.onap.org/job/offline-installer-master-yaml-lint/22/ )\n\nLogs: https://logs.onap.org/production/vex-yul-ecomp-jenkins-1/offline-installer-master-yaml-lint/22",
        "patchset_number": 1
